land terecht. Wat een geluk bij een ongeluk. Toch?</font><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 248); font-weight: 700;\">De smokkel</span><br><font color=\"#f8f8f8\">Deze kamer zal je niet snel vergeten! Smokkelen is het illegaal over de grens brengen van goederen, heb jij dit stiekem wel eens gedaan? Hier moet je samen met je team de douaniers te slim af zijn.</font><br><br><font color=\"#f8f8f8\">Wilt u RESERVEREN? Ga naar de speciale </font><u style=\"\"><a href=\"/reserveren\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\"><font color=\"#ffffff\"><b>reserveren</b></font></a>&nbsp;</u><font color=\"#F8F8F8\" style=\"color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\">pagina</font></p></div><div class=\'edit-block\' onclick=\'editBlock(this)\' id=\'edit-block-yyda6\'><i  class=\'edit-block-icon bx bx-edit\'></i></div><div class=\'cancel-block\' onclick=\'removeblock(this)\' id=\'edit-block-yyda6\'><i  class=\'remove-block-icon bx bx-trash\'></i></div></div></div></div><div class=\"delete-columns-row\" id=\"kbu16\" onclick=\"deleteColumn(this)\"><i class=\"delete-columns-row-icon bx bx-trash\"></i></div><div class=\"edit-parent-column\" id=\"kbu16\" onclick=\"editColumnRow(this)\"><i class=\"edit-column-row-icon bx bx-edit\"></i></div><div class=\'sortable-handle\' wire:sortable.handle><i class=\'edit-column-row-icon bx bx-move\'></i></div></div>',0,'kbu16',1,'2026-01-13 15:25:15','2026-01-13 15:25:15'),(1439,'<div class=\"full-width-box\" wire:sortable.item=\"hbgg9\" wire:key=\"hbgg9\" id=\"full-width-box-hbgg9\" style=\"background-color: rgb(77, 54, 49); max-width: 100%; margin: 0px;\"> <div class=\"container row-container\" id=\"container-hbgg9\" style=\"padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;\"><div id=\'d16f7\' class=\'two-columns-row row added-block-row\'><div class=\"col-12 col-md-6 added-column added-column-2\" style=\"padding: 0px;\" id=\"bhg81\"><div class=\'edit-columns-row\' onclick=\'editColumn(this)\'><i class=\'edit-columns-row-icon bx bx-edit\'></i></div><div class=\"block-texteditor block-val